---
layout: base.njk
---

<style>
  .post-header {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .post-eyecatch {
    background: var(--green-light);
    height: 200px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 5rem;
  }
  .post-header-body { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .post-meta {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .post-cat-badge {
    background: var(--green-light);
    color: var(--green);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .post-title {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* 記事本文 */
  .post-body {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .post-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--white);
    background: var(--green);
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
  }
  .post-body h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--green);
    padding: 0.4rem 0 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--green);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem;
  }
  .post-body p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .post-body ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .post-body li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .post-body hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 2px dashed var(--green-light);
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .post-cta {
    background: var(--green-light);
    border: 2px solid var(--green);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .post-cta p { margin-bottom: 0.8rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }

  /* 戻るリンク */
  .post-back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--green);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--green);
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .post-back:hover { background: var(--green-light); text-decoration: none; }
</style>

<article>
  <div class="post-header">
    <div class="post-eyecatch">🧘</div>
    <div class="post-header-body">
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span>{{ date | dateJP }}</span>
        <span class="post-cat-badge">ヨガ体験談</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="post-title">{{ title }}</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="post-body">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>

  <div class="post-cta">
    <p>💚 この記事が参考になったら、まず無料体験から始めてみてください🍀</p>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--text-muted);">※ アフィリエイトリンクはこちらに入ります</p>
  </div>

  <a href="/" class="post-back">← 記事一覧に戻る</a>
</article>
